OL,3,CCouncil apologises to motorists for
OL,4,Cincorrectly issuing parking fines
OL,6,FReading Borough Council has apologised
OL,7,Fto motorists for incorrectly issuing
OL,8,Fparking fines over a number of years.
OL,10,FThe council discovered the Traffic
OL,11,FRegulation Order (TRO) on sections of
OL,12,Fthe East Reading Red Route and some
OL,13,Fparking restrictions in other
OL,14,Flocations are unenforceable.
OL,16,FA total of 6,136 penalty charge
OL,17,Fnotices (PCNs) were incorrectly issued
OL,18,Fand paid primarily between July 2018
OL,19,Fand 2024 with some dating back to 2013.
