OL,3,CCouncil apologises to motorists for
OL,4,Cincorrectly issuing parking fines
OL,6,FIt says drivers who have paid these
OL,7,Fpenalties will be reimbursed.
OL,9,FFor motorists that have been subject
OL,10,Fincorrectly to a debt recovery
OL,11,Fprocess, the council says it will
OL,12,Fcontact individuals directly, telling
OL,13,Fthem how the repayment will be made
OL,14,Fwith interest.
