OL,3,CCouncil apologises to motorists for
OL,4,Cincorrectly issuing parking fines
OL,6,FJackie Yates, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FReading Borough Council, said: "I
OL,8,Fsincerely apologise to all motorists
OL,9,Fand residents who have been affected
OL,10,Fby these errors and urge them to visit
OL,11,Fthe Council's website so that we can
OL,12,Freimburse them.
OL,14,F"We have made the reimbursement
OL,15,Fprocess as easy as possible for people
OL,16,Fwho have been wrongly issued with
OL,17,Fpenalty charge notices, whilst
OL,18,Fensuring we have appropriate
OL,19,Fverification checks in place.
