OL,3,CCouncil apologises to motorists for
OL,4,Cincorrectly issuing parking fines
OL,6,F"Parking enforcement action was
OL,7,Fsuspended as soon as the Council
OL,8,Fbecame aware of the specific TRO
OL,9,Fissues and further action is being
OL,10,Ftaken to ensure that the circumstances
OL,11,Fwhich led to this situation don't
OL,12,Fhappen again.
OL,14,F"On behalf of the council, I sincerely
OL,15,Fapologise to motorists for the
OL,16,Fdistress and inconvenience caused."
OL,18,FThe errors came to light when a member
OL,19,Fof staff reported a defect on the East
OL,20,FReading Red Route.
