OL,3,CCouncil apologises to motorists for
OL,4,Cincorrectly issuing parking fines
OL,6,FA wider investigation was carried out
OL,7,Fto review whether there were further
OL,8,Fissues with TROs and a small number
OL,9,Fwere found to be incorrect.
OL,11,FMotorists who think they have been
OL,12,Fincorrectly issued with a PCN can
OL,13,Fclaim a refund via the council's
OL,14,Fwebsite from Wednesday 16 October
OL,15,Ffollowing agreement of the Scheme by
OL,16,Fthe council on Tuesday 15 October.
